Class BankAccount

    • BankAccount
  • public class BankAccount
extends java.lang.Object

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor Description
      BankAccount()
      OVERLOADED CONSTRUCTOR METHODS Constructor that takes no arguments, creating accounts for a user with $0.00 each.
      BankAccount​(double checkingBalance, double savingsBalance)
      Constructor that takes 2 arguments (double checkingBalance, double savingsBalance), creating checking and savings accounts for a user with a starting balance equal to the checkingBalance and savingsBalance arguments.
      BankAccount​(java.lang.String accountType, double initialBalance)
      Constructor that takes 2 arguments (String accountType, double initialBalance), creating checking and savings accounts for a user with a starting balance of initialBalance in the specified accountType (either "checking" or "savings") and a balance of $0.00 in the other account created.
